<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4438155>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 8. Levinsenia marmarensis (ESFM-POL/2013-1177).A, Dorsal view of anterior end of body; B, Anterio-dorsal view of prostomium and first chaetigers; C, Anterio-dorsal view of lateral part of prostomium, arrow pointing the bulge on posteriolateral side of prostomium; D, Anterio-ventral view of lateral part of prostomium, left arrow pointing the bulge on posterio-lat- eral side of prostomium; E, First three branchial chaetigers; F, Modified neurochaetae from posterior chaetiger; G, Notopodium from first chaetiger with lateral sense organ; H, Notopodium from middle branchial chaetiger with notopodial postchaetal lobe, lateral sense organ and dorso-lateral irregular pores. Scale bar: A, 128 µm; B, 37 µm; C, 33 µm; D, µm 46; E, 40 µm; F, 12 µm; G, 11 µm; H, 20 µm. Abbreviations: ant, anterior region; bran, branchia; dlip, dorso-lateral irregular pores; lso, lateral sense organ; csal, ciliary slits of anterior lips; ntpcl, notopodial postchaetal lobe; post, posterior region." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4438155/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4438153>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 7. Levinsenia marmarensis (ESFM-POL/2013-1175).A, Dorsal view of anterior end of body, stained with Shirlastain- A; B, Modified neurochaeta from chaetiger 70. Scale bar: A, 363 µm; B, 22 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4438153/files/figure.png" .

